.head 3 +  Function: CustDepositReqd
.head 4 -  Description: Check the Deposit_reqd flag of Customer_Master for the given cust_no
and return FALSE if the customer isnt required to pay a deposit or 
if the customer is required to pay a deposit and has already done so
for the year in question.  A TRUE return means that we need to get
deposit details for this customer.
