.head 4 +  ! Double-click to expand these comments.
.head 5 -  ! CHANGES, frmOrderDetails has had the problem with allocated check box fixed
  and the sale cat data field problem fixed also.
  on adding a order in frmOrderDetails the automatic click on pbItems has been
  removed.
.head 5 -  ! 15/2/95 Customer contacts and master for orchardists bug is fixed
.head 5 -  ! 15/2/95 Deleting a customer will now check that he can be deleted and delete him
from everywhere he needs to be leaving history though 
.head 5 -  ! 20/2/95 Generating a credit note falling down when no of trees < no credited
.head 5 -  ! message disabling going to orders from frmCustomer ( customer details )
.head 5 -  ! 20/2/95 Bug in combining rods and trees in dlgQitem fixed - shouldnt combine
.head 5 -  ! 22/2/95 custadd.apl, custcont.apl, regions.apl, frcodes.apl, regmeets.apl,
  meetaddr.apl, pcodes.apl, custtype.apl, gcofrm.apl, barcode.apl, orddets.apl,
  custdets.apl, nparfusl.apl, ordsload.apl where created and this program
  is now using them.
.head 5 -  ! 22/2/95     94 totals into customer details listing fixed
.head 5 -  ! 23/2/95     changing order, now sets the ack_flag and Conf_flag to 'N' for one
  on the customers orders to force acknowledgments and confirmations to print
  out again.  Also if year is changed a order from both years orders have the 
  ack and conf flags set to 'N'.
.head 5 -  ! 23/2/95     frmOrderDets, frmGCOrderForm, dlgQItem, dlgCancel were commented
  out with related internal functions as these are redundant and in future can be
  deleted from the program to make it smaller.
.head 5 -  ! 23/2/95    problem found with getshipaddress logic not getting a address when
  selecting a item to order and therefore the check for prohibition fails on 
  prohibited items.  Fixed, but should be looked at to recheck the logic in 
  get ship address.
.head 5 -  ! 27/2/95 Denormalising code put in - DO NOT put into live until data denormalised 
.head 5 -  ! 27/2/95 Myfunc.apl has had the print reports and other windows taken out into
  seperate APLs.
.head 5 -  ! 28/2/95 Local frmOrderDetails check for not increasing conf_amt past ord_amt
  or conf_amt < 0 like negatives not allowed messages are in place.
.head 5 -  ! 1/3/95 region look up from postcode implemented in custdets.apl ( frmCustomer )
.head 5 -  ! 2/3/95 various customer checks put in and stops when going to add order
.head 5 -  ! 3/3/95 order date validation put in where checking for > current date and sequence
of screens from frmQcustomer changed
.head 5 -  !
.head 5 -  ! 3/3/95 BIG NOTE acknowledgments have changed.  a new apl replaced the
  printack.apl called prntack2.apl.  It used a report called ACKOLD.QRP if this version
  is going live then rename the report and the file name in the prntack2.apl
.head 5 -  ! 15/3/95 Dont allow transfer of orders if already invoiced.  Needs testing
.head 5 -  ! 15/3/95 Dont allow two live invoice runs.
.head 5 -  ! 15/3/95 Update load customer invoiced flag when invoiced in this program
.head 5 -  ! 27/4/95 Check for pulled orders in invoicing allowing for advance claims but also 
doing the check prior to in the middle of processing orders
.head 5 -  !
.head 5 -  ! 29/5/95 INVOICING SAME AS LOADS AGAIN AND POS SENDING IS ASSUMED AND NOT ASKED
.head 5 -  ! 23/5/95 Invoicing calculate freight charges on customer basis is implemented
.head 5 -  ! 22/11/95 Credit note fix for coral
.head 5 -  ! Uninvoicing changes put in on 15/1/96
.head 5 -  !
