.head 3 +  Function: MySumOrdConf
.head 4 -  Description: To sum the ordered and confirmed values as label charges require these
and freight charges is now done on an order basis not a customer basis
.head 4 +  Returns
.head 5 -  Boolean:
.head 4 +  Parameters
.head 5 -  Number: nCustNo
.head 5 -  Number: nYear
.head 5 -  ! sDisplayOrderType = 'ALL' OR 'BARE_ROOTED' OR 'CONTAINERISED'
